column16: Gregory Polanco flies out to left fielder Clint Robinson.
Pedro Florimon singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Clint Robinson.
Francisco Cervelli homers (5) on a fly ball to center field.
Wilmer Flores grounds out, shortstop Ian Desmond to first baseman Clint Robinson.   Ruben Tejada scores.    Daniel Murphy to 3rd.    Lucas Duda to 2nd.
Lucas Duda walks.   Ruben Tejada to 3rd.    Daniel Murphy to 2nd.
